{"tid":581519,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★金鐘站天花空調喉漏水變水舞間","createTime":"2018-03-05T11:54:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-05T12:06:31.000Z","uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9a8dfdb4e1c7e936030068e37de6312d0c62a1a6","tid":581519,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T11:54:56.000Z","msg":"【18:00】港鐵發言人表示，今早約11時45分，金鐘站荃灣線往荃灣方向月台近車尾位置，一條空調系統喉管管身出現漏水，受影響範圍的6度幕門需暫時停用，為減低對乘客的影響，乘客暫時使用其他車門上落車。港鐵派員清理地面積水，安排喉管搶修。期間，金鐘及中環站加派人手，列車上亦廣播提醒乘客使用其他車門上落車，列車服務不受影響。至下午2時55分，漏水已處理好，月台幕門可恢復運作，工程人員將在今晚收車後維修。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵金鐘站荃灣線往荃灣方向一號月台，下午有天花突然漏水，月台布滿水漬，港鐵派出多名人員清理積水，並進行緊急維修，以帆布圍封受影響位置。受漏水影響，列車進站後，近車尾月台的6道幕門需暫時封閉，乘客不得進出，經搶修後幕門已恢復運作。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180305/bkn-20180305162327038-0305_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180305%2Fbkn-20180305162327038-0305_00822_001.html&d=WlnnxHFi7%2F5XORf1i7aNZFzEg0sy7MJ6GkP0ogsbSqo%3D&h=0628458f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180305/bkn-20180305162327038-0305_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27c333567dadc7086f0a84abecb8a7c3dff82548","tid":581519,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T11:55:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180305/photo/bkn-20180305162327038-0305_00822_001_01b.jpg?20180305183656\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180305%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180305162327038-0305_00822_001_01b.jpg%3F20180305183656&h=b46bfc08&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"881e0aded56ae0d7b977b0d099ce94c0ffe87a44","tid":581519,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedB